THQ Nordic is set to release their report for the first quarter of 2018 on Wednesday the 16th of May.  Q1 will be the first quarter reported after the significant acquisition of Koch Media, as such the sales and results are harder to estimate than usual due to many moving components. We view the overall performance of the Group and communication about the future as more critical than estimate deviance.

